Text.Value: ホワイトヘブンエリア１

Dialogue.Value: [This place....]
[Ugh，all these trees....,Sorry Alice，you were saying,something?]
[Nevermind，it’s nothing....]
[Alright.,Let’s just get our answers and,leave，my nose is killing me.]
[And so deep in the Undernet....,Who could have done,something like this?]
[Is this a garden....?]
[A series of barriers completely,blocks off access past this,point.]
[A message is inscribed in the,frontmost barrier:]
[ THE WAY IS SHUT, SEEK THE MISTRESS AND, GAIN PASSAGE BEYOND]
[A message is inscribed into,the air before the barrier:]
[THE WAY SHALL OPEN TO,ONE WHO KNOWS ALL,ON HEAVEN AND EARTH]
[DISPLAY UNDERSTANDING]
[Great，now what?]
[If you want me to sit here and try,every 5-digit code，we’re going,to have words，Alice.]
[“Knows all on Heaven and,Earth”....,....Shanghai，do you think....?]
[....The Sage?,That does sound like his thing.,Can’t hurt to try，anyways.]
[Time to go find an old man.,Let’s get out of here，Alice.]
[....Shanghai，I don’t think--]
[You’d be surprised by how,many people use that as their,password.]
[If you find a lost briefcase，try,it out，it just might open!]
[I don’t think you should be,opening someone else’s,briefcase in the first place!]
[....Shanghai，are you alright?,Do you want to talk about it?]
[No.,Let’s just hurry up and find,whoever’s in charge here.]
[Find them， and.... ask them,some questions.]
